Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:14.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs90}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好 欢迎收看Grand Tour\N{\fs90}The Grand Tour Hello, and welcome to The Grand Tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:23.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个星期我们来到了纳什维尔\N{\fs90}which this week comes to you from Nashville!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:24.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这里\N{\fs90}- There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:30.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个 这个城市是以纳什将军命名\N{\fs90}It was er... It's a city that was named after General Nash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,战争英雄 把英国佬赶出了这里\N{\fs90}Big war hero, kicked the British out.
