Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些是前五\N{\fs90}This is the top five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:51.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,仔细看看 这就是所谓的独立 挺好的嘛\N{\fs90}There you go, that's independence... working well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:54.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,丰田  本田  丰田  日产  本田\N{\fs90}Toyota, Honda, Toyota, Nissan, Honda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,那这段时间底特律究竟都造了什么\N{\fs90}So what is actually made in Detroit these days, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:02:01.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,估计 他们就是种些有机豆子吧\N{\fs90}Er... Well, mostly they just grow sustainable organic peas beans
