Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,市政社区农场\N{\fs90}municipal farms for the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们之所以来到纳什维尔\N{\fs90}Now, the reason we've come to Nashville
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上很简单\N{\fs90}is very simple, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我走遍了美国50个州\N{\fs90}It's because I've been to all 50 of the US states,
