Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,摩城 摩城\N{\fs90}Motown... Motown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是三分种热度的疯人疯语\N{\fs90}is just three minutes of jangly nonsense.
