Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 在这之前\N{\fs90}Anyway, before all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们有过一场小争执\N{\fs90}we've been having a bit of a debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,我说过 你不需要买宝马M3\N{\fs90}You see, I say you don't need to buy a BMW M3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:07.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为少花九万二 你可以选择捷豹XE S\N{\fs90}because for £11,000 less you can have a Jaguar XE S,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,而它更好开\N{\fs90}which is nicer to drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,更舒服而且一样快\N{\fs90}more comfortable and just as fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:12.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它并没有一样快 -它有\N{\fs90}- It isn't just as fast. - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不它没有 -它们都能跑到250km/h\N{\fs90}- No, it isn't. - They both do 155mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是因为宝马将速度锁在了250km/h\N{\fs90}Yes, because the BMW has been electronically limited to 155.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,对于捷豹 那速度就是极限\N{\fs90}The Jag is just... limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不好意思打断一下\N{\fs90}- Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我的两个同事都错了\N{\fs90}It's just that both my colleagues are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为如果你想要一辆又小又快的轿车\N{\fs90}Because if you want a small, fast saloon car,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,你绝对应该拥有的是\N{\fs90}what you absolutely have to have--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你要开始\N{\fs90}If you're gonna start going on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,说起阿尔法罗密欧Giulia Quadrifoglio\N{\fs90}about that Alfa Romeo Giulia Quadrifoglio,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:36.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就把这支笔插进你眼睛里\N{\fs90}I am gonna stab you in the eye with this pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不 他的确 -很多次\N{\fs90}- No, he's-- - A number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,他是对的 阿尔法罗密欧已经30年\N{\fs90}He's right. Alfa Romeo have not made a decent car
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,没造一辆好车了\N{\fs90}for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯  -嗯个头\N{\fs90}- Erm... - "Erm" nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们要回到重点上\N{\fs90}because we need to get back to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:47.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯和我决定\N{\fs90}James and I have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候让捷豹宝马分高下了\N{\fs90}it was time to sort out this Jaguar-BMW debate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:53.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,在苏格兰进行一场合适的老派道路测试\N{\fs90}with a proper old-school road test in Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好 欢迎来到威尔士\N{\fs90}Hello, and welcome to Wales,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:09.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我和所有的拍摄团队来到这里\N{\fs90}where I've come with all of our film crews and this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:15.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,以及这辆崭新的阿尔法.罗密欧Giulia... Quadrifoglio\N{\fs90}the brand-new Alfa Romeo Giulia... Quadrifoglio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该是这么读\N{\fs90}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,无所谓啦\N{\fs90}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们看看它究竟如何\N{\fs90}Let's and see what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:30.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果它是辆典型的阿尔法罗密欧\N{\fs90}Now, for this to be a proper Alfa Romeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:34.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,它一定会有些毛病\N{\fs90}there must be... something wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,试想\N{\fs90}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,某人对母亲很孝顺\N{\fs90}A person who's kind to his mother
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,准时 清醒又穿着得体 他就是奥迪\N{\fs90}and punctual and sober and well-dressed, he's an Audi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,没人想要这样的朋友\N{\fs90}And nobody wants a friend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:49.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果要和一辆车建立一段关系\N{\fs90}If you're going to form a relationship with a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果想建立一条纽带\N{\fs90}if you're gonna develop a bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车就需要有一些人格特质\N{\fs90}it's got to have human qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,而如果它有这些\N{\fs90}And if it's gonna have human qualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,那它必定会有缺陷\N{\fs90}it's got to have faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:03.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车 我很高兴地说 有一个大问题\N{\fs90}And this car, I'm delighted to say, has a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道他们是怎么设计这个的\N{\fs90}I don't know quite how they've managed this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我不太容易下车\N{\fs90}but it's not very easy to get out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有门柱 那里有方向盘\N{\fs90}You've got this pillar here, then the wheel here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,这俩之间\N{\fs90}and there isn't enough of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有足够空间\N{\fs90}of a gap between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 等等\N{\fs90}Hang on a minute. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧这多有"阿尔法罗密欧"的性格啊\N{\fs90}How Alfa Romeo is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们把门装错了位置 它应该在\N{\fs90}They put the door in the wrong place. It should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,它应该在更后面\N{\fs90}It should be further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,太牛了\N{\fs90}That is brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有更多\N{\fs90}There's more, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是一辆很好看的车\N{\fs90}It's not a particularly handsome car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,轮子太小了\N{\fs90}The wheels are too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,处于一些原因\N{\fs90}And for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们选择将车的前面\N{\fs90}they've chosen to make the front
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,看上去像沃尔斯利\N{\fs90}look like a Wolseley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,最近一段时间 詹姆斯说的很对\N{\fs90}Now, in the recent past-- James is quite right--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,阿尔法有他们的缺陷\N{\fs90}Alfas have had their faults
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,也没有好的方面来弥补\N{\fs90}and then no good bits to compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们只是用错驱动轮的菲亚特\N{\fs90}They've just been wrong-wheel-drive Fiats
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,把"菲亚特"这个词划掉\N{\fs90}with the word "Fiat" crossed out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,再用蜡笔写上了"阿尔法罗密欧"\N{\fs90}and "Alfa Romeo" written  in crayon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,那辆车 显然\N{\fs90}That, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,是完全不同的生物\N{\fs90}...that's a very different animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:40.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车太棒了\N{\fs90}This is a fabulous car,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,如此伟大\N{\fs90}an epic car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,大概因为它是法拉利458设计师的\N{\fs90}Probably because it's the love child of the same man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:47.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,溺子\N{\fs90}who engineered the Ferrari 458.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:58.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,他为它装上了碳纤维传动轴\N{\fs90}He's given it a carbon-fibre propshaft,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,碳纤维车顶\N{\fs90}a carbon-fibre roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,碳纤维引擎盖\N{\fs90}a carbon-fibre bonnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,一颗正经的限滑差速器\N{\fs90}a proper limited-slip differential,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,得心应手的转向 以及聪明的变速箱\N{\fs90}telepathic steering and a clever gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这车最令人叫绝的\N{\fs90}But the most impressive bit of this car
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:16.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,是那台2.9升涡轮增压的V6发动机\N{\fs90}is its turbocharged 2.9L V6 engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:22.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,每当你关车门 发动机都会一起抖动\N{\fs90}An engine that wobbles when you close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,厉害了 快看\N{\fs90}That is brilliant. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:28.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你家奥迪肯定没法这样吧\N{\fs90}You don't get that sort of thing from an Audi, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,法拉利呢\N{\fs90}Ferrari, which, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,与阿尔法罗密欧同属一个公司\N{\fs90}is part of the same company as Alfa Romeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们特别指出\N{\fs90}is very keen to point out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:38.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是去掉两个汽缸的\N{\fs90}that this is not the engine they use in the California
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚上的那台引擎\N{\fs90}with two cylinders removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们说两台引擎纯属巧合\N{\fs90}They say it's a complete coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:46.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,拥有同样的缸径冲程比和气缸夹角\N{\fs90}that both engines have the same bore/stroke and V-angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们坚持发动机是阿尔法罗密欧自己造的\N{\fs90}They're adamant that this is all Alfa Romeo's own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fs90}So, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们信了\N{\fs90}It is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,真是台好引擎啊\N{\fs90}And what work it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:06.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,503匹的马力\N{\fs90}You get 503 brake horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:11.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,这比宝马M3多出60匹 60匹啊\N{\fs90}That is 60 more than you get from a BMW M3. 60!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,比起那辆捷豹\N{\fs90}It's 175 more
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,多出了175匹\N{\fs90}than you get from that Jag
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,要不是我站出来力挽狂澜\N{\fs90}that James would be droning on about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在詹姆斯还在吹那破车\N{\fs90}had I not stepped in and saved the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后就是这车的转速\N{\fs90}And then there's the way it revs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\fs90}Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:42.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,大多数涡轮发动机到了高转都会有点虚\N{\fs90}Most turbocharged engines are a bit wheezy at the top end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,但由于这车的双涡管涡轮\N{\fs90}but because the twin-scroll turbo in this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:48.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,在发动机的V字夹角处放置\N{\fs90}is mounted in the V of the engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:51.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,和法拉利的加利福尼亚一样\N{\fs90}...just like it is in a Ferrari California,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,巧了\N{\fs90}coincidentally,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,转速一直到红区\N{\fs90}the rev counter is still a blur
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,毫不拖沓\N{\fs90}right up to the red zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这引擎真是\N{\fs90}This engine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,大师级的\N{\fs90}...it's a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs90}An absolute gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 这车或许长得像辆沃斯利\N{\fs90}So, while this may look like a Wolseley,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,跑起来可一点也不像\N{\fs90}it certainly doesn't go like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:39.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,它的极速可达到每小时307公里\N{\fs90}It has a top speed, in fact, of 191mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车\N{\fs90}What this car is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实就是法拉利的\N{\fs90}is a Ferrari...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,四门情趣诱惑版\N{\fs90}...wearing four-door sensi-panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:55.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,说到这 我就要提这车的绝活了\N{\fs90}And that brings me onto this car's party piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,在常规时速下 这车非常安静平顺\N{\fs90}At normal speeds, it's very quiet and very civilised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,即便这车的轮胎\N{\fs90}And even though it's running on wheels
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,小的像是沙发底下的轮子一样\N{\fs90}that appear to have come off the bottom of a sofa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,乘坐还是很舒服\N{\fs90}it's very comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,即便你按下这里\N{\fs90}even if you push this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,让悬挂变硬 也不会不舒服\N{\fs90}you put it in bumpy-suspension mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,唯一我还没试过的模式\N{\fs90}The only setting I haven't yet tried
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这个赛道模式\N{\fs90}is this one-- "race".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得我该试试\N{\fs90}But I think I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,不幸的是\N{\fs90}Sadly, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,还没等我找到赛道\N{\fs90}before I found somewhere to try it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就接到了电话\N{\fs90}I received a telephone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 什么事？\N{\fs90}Oh, no. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:36.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德打来的 -你是把我们的摄制组劫走了吗\N{\fs90}- Hammond. - Have you got our film crew somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:40.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -你们是在拍阿尔法吗\N{\fs90}- Yes, I have. - Are you using them to film an Alfa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的  -你现在在哪\N{\fs90}- Yes, I am. - Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,-威尔士 -威尔士?!\N{\fs90}- Wales. - Wales?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,你凭什么安排我们去苏格兰\N{\fs90}You can't just arrange that we go to Scotland
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后自己去威尔士\N{\fs90}and then disappear off to Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没告诉你们去苏格兰\N{\fs90}I didn't tell you to go to Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,是你们自己决定要去的\N{\fs90}You decided to go to Scotland on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们大老远的跑到苏格兰\N{\fs90}We've come all the way to Scotland
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,来做这两辆车的评测\N{\fs90}to do this with these two cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,明明说好了 你却硬要搞\N{\fs90}This is the test. You trying to shoehorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道阿尔法罗密欧给这个世界带来了很多快乐\N{\fs90}It's wonderful there are Alfa Romeos in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:02.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也知道这车非常值得我们喜爱\N{\fs90}That's a lovely thing that we can all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,你个人觉得阿尔法罗密欧有多好\N{\fs90}It doesn't matter how good you think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:07.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,并不重要 这是汽车节目\N{\fs90}the Alfa Romeo is. This is a car programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,概念 希望 都是虚的\N{\fs90}Concepts, dreams, imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,苏格兰 两辆靠谱的 有价值的车\N{\fs90}...Scotland, with two cars that are credible, relevant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,万众瞩目的 能跑并且真实存在的车\N{\fs90}important, work and are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我和摄制组抵达赛道时\N{\fs90}They were still shouting at me as I arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,他俩还在那朝我哔哔\N{\fs90}with all of the film crews at our track.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,那块你十年来一直想要\N{\fs90}...itch, that you've managed to scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,解开的心结\N{\fs90}over the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就纳闷了 为啥\N{\fs90}I don't know how. Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,信号不行了\N{\fs90}It's breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:27.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 我掉线了\N{\fs90}Oh, I've lost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,赛道模式\N{\fs90}Race mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,走起\N{\fs90}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,在赛道模式下 一切都紧张了起来\N{\fs90}In race mode, everything is in a tensed-up state:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,油门响应 离合器换挡 转向\N{\fs90}the throttle response, the gearbox, the steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且牵引力控制系统关闭了\N{\fs90}And the traction control is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,这让它\N{\fs90}This has now been transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,从一辆好车\N{\fs90}from something that was brilliant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,变成了一辆摄人心魄的车\N{\fs90}into something that is sensational.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:42.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然了 你平时肯定不会用到赛道模式\N{\fs90}Of course, you'd never drive in race mode on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:46.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像你永远不会带着你的手表上太空\N{\fs90}in the same way you'd never take your wristwatch into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:51.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是知道它在太空也能用 心里会很爽\N{\fs90}But it's nice to know that it would still work if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车也是如此\N{\fs90}And this does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车无所不能\N{\fs90}Oh, boy, this does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:04.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,我总会说 没拥有过一辆阿尔法罗密欧\N{\fs90}I've always said you can't be a true petrolhead
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就不能算是个真车迷\N{\fs90}until you've owned an Alfa Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,但问题是 我其实一直都知道\N{\fs90}And the trouble is, I've always known
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,当今没有一辆阿尔法罗密欧\N{\fs90}there's no Alfa Romeo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,能吸引真车迷去购买\N{\fs90}a true petrolhead would actually want to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,但现在有了\N{\fs90}There is now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,现真有了\N{\fs90}Oh, there is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:34.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我决定做一件事\N{\fs90}And so I decided to do something I've never done
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,这在我整个试车生涯中从没做过\N{\fs90}with any car I've ever filmed in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,我决定 试车结束后\N{\fs90}I decided, when the test was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,去最近的阿尔法罗密欧经销商\N{\fs90}to go to the nearest Alfa Romeo dealer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,买一辆回家\N{\fs90}...and buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,-咋了 -你个混蛋\N{\fs90}- What? - You total cock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,你抢了我们的片子\N{\fs90}You stole our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,不能这么说吧\N{\fs90}Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,你最后没真买一辆吧\N{\fs90}You didn't actually buy one, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 因为我没想好\N{\fs90}Well, no, cos I couldn't make my mind up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,是买4C还是买它\N{\fs90}between that and the 4C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就像是猩猩回到笼子里\N{\fs90}It was like watching an ape return to its cage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,发现里面有一个苹果和一个香蕉\N{\fs90}and finding there was an apple and a banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我喜欢苹果 但是也喜欢香蕉\N{\fs90}"Oh, I like apple, but I like bananas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我是要苹果呢还是香蕉呢\N{\fs90}So do I want the apple or a banana?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实可以都要的\N{\fs90}You would have had both, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 这车非常棒\N{\fs90}Hammond, that car is brilliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且售价只要6万磅\N{\fs90}and it only costs £60,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,是 但是杰里米 你说这些都没用\N{\fs90}Yeah, but honestly, Jeremy, that doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,就算阿尔法罗密欧发布一摊狗屎\N{\fs90}If Alfa Romeo launched a dog turd,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:44.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,你也会说很棒的\N{\fs90}you'd say it was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,它真的很棒 我不骗你\N{\fs90}It is! I'm not making it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,你都听到和看到了 它确实是辆好车\N{\fs90}You heard it. You saw it. It's a fantastic car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管了 下面我们要看看\N{\fs90}Anyway, listen, we must find out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个四什么玩意的在埃博拉赛道上能跑多快\N{\fs90}how fast the Quadri-thingy goes round the Eboladrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就意味着要把车交给一个人\N{\fs90}That, of course, means handing it over
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,他认为网球这项运动\N{\fs90}to a man who thinks that tennis is something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,是斯大林发明的\N{\fs90}that was invented by Stalin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,这星期他算是本土作战\N{\fs90}He's actually a local boy this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,他家就是隔壁州的\N{\fs90}from the next state along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,有请老美\N{\fs90}It's the American!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,快看\N{\fs90}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,即使是他也会喜欢\N{\fs90}And even he will enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,这台迷人的车子\N{\fs90}this magnificent machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定\N{\fs90}I'm sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出发了\N{\fs90}And he's off with a glorious bark
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着那动人的V6的一声雄壮的嘶吼\N{\fs90}and a pop from that sensational V6.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,今天赛道好湿啊\N{\fs90}Oh, it's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:26.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 阿尔法罗密欧朱丽叶四蹦子\N{\fs90}OK. Alfa Romeo Julie Quad Bike
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,之类的什么鬼\N{\fs90}something or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不会说 根本不会念\N{\fs90}I can't say it, can't pronounce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,也不大喜欢开\N{\fs90}I don't really like driving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fs90}Oh, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:40.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,听说高个子觉得这是辆好车\N{\fs90}So, the tall one thinks this is a good car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得他小时候脑袋被磕过\N{\fs90}I still think he was dropped on his head as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,是 可我至少我不会戴着牛仔帽去婚礼\N{\fs90}Yeah, but at least I don't wear a cowboy hat to weddings.
