Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可能是最精彩的一圈了\N{\fs90}This could be the single greatest lap we'll ever see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,你瞎说什么呢\N{\fs90}What are you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身非常平衡\N{\fs90}It's beautifully balanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,大脚油门\N{\fs90}hard on the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身有点不稳 有些转向过度\N{\fs90}A bit of a wobble there! Some oversteer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的设计意图就是这样\N{\fs90}but it was designed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,才不是呢\N{\fs90}No, it wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,别说话 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Stop saying things, Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我忙着呢\N{\fs90}I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是一辆\N{\fs90}This is just a BMW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,喜欢喝花哨咖啡的人开的宝马\N{\fs90}for people who like fancy coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:12.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这是给有品位和有眼光的人开的宝马\N{\fs90}No, it's a BMW for people with taste and discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这是给傻子开的宝马\N{\fs90}No, it's a BMW for idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:15.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 安静\N{\fs90}Hammond, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看它在经过\N{\fs90}Look at the way it's dealing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,老奶房的时候的样子\N{\fs90}with Old Lady's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,一点问题都没有\N{\fs90}Almost no problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在他可以彻底放开\N{\fs90}Now he can really turn it up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲刺一段冲向变电站\N{\fs90}for the sprint to Substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这动力 这血统\N{\fs90}Such power! Such pedigree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这渣渣 -安静\N{\fs90}- Such bollocks. - Just be quiet!
