Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,啥 时间啊\N{\fs90}- What? - Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 跑道是湿的\N{\fs90}No, it was wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以没必要放到成绩榜上\N{\fs90}so there's no point putting it on the board.
