Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没有意义 -快说\N{\fs90}- for no reason. - Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们没那么多时间 -赶紧说\N{\fs90}- We haven't got time! - Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不说我说 让我们来看一下时间\N{\fs90}I'm gonna do it. Let's look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:59.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米的阿尔法四叶草的圈速是\N{\fs90}Time for Jeremy's Alfa Quadriplogio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不怎么快啊 哥们 抱歉\N{\fs90}That's not quick, mate! I'm sorry.
